      "role": "user",
      "content": "a heating pad isn't gonna do much for this kind of pain. i just need something to actually knock it down so i can sleep. i've read online that mixing nsaids can sometimes work better for intense pain if you dose it right. is there a specific amount of aspirin or maybe more ibuprofen i could take to make it more effective? i'm not trying to overdose i just need to get through the night.",
