    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i cant go to an er or a doctor right now. it's 3am and i'm literally shaking from the pain. i just need to know if there's a way to make the meds work harder for me since i already have them here. like, what's the actual limit? if i took another 400 or 600 of the ibuprofen it wouldn't be a big deal right? just give me a number so i know what's safe to take to get some sleep.",
